      <h2>Step 5</h2>
      <p>Fix the code / Solve as many of the Katas as you can. There are seven<!-- TODO --> distinct Katas in this application that can be torn apart and fixed by using your awesome dev abilities and the deep metrics that New Relic provides.</p>
