        <ol>
      		<li>Generate traffic a.k.a. click around</li>
      		<li>Discover a slow page</li>
      		<li>Investigate the problem (using New Relic)</li>
      		<li>Resolve with code changes</li>
      		<li>
            Push the revised code to your GitHub repo and then pull (using "git pull") from the root of your application on your EC2 instance.
            <br>
            <em style="margin-left: 1em;">Repeat...</em>
          </li>
      	</ol>
  		</p>
